(11663, 1, '2017-02-06 11:14:20', '2017-02-06 11:14:20', '[vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\"][vc_column][rev_slider_vc alias=\"about-us\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<p class=\"justify\">To start with, Monochrome isn’t a ‘we’, it’s a ‘me’. I am the Owner, Founder, and Head Cook and Bottle Washer here. It is very much a one-woman-show, and I’d like to talk to you for a moment about why that is such a good thing for you.</p>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">I specialise in providing not just personalised but personal service. I’m the only person you’ll talk to on the phone, the only one who will handle your account, and the only one responsible for giving you outstanding results. When I am working on your account, I am working in your account! When you deal with Monochrome Marketing, you are dealing with me, personally, every time, and I absolutely promise to do right by you on every single task, great or small.</p>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">Now, that is not to say what I do isn’t entirely of a professional caliber, or that you’ll get anything less than state of the art, truly exceptional services. I may only have been in business for myself since 2012, but I have many years of marketing experience under my belt, and I have learned from some of the most respected names in the industry – what better way to become one myself, after all?</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'About Us New', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about-us-new', '', '', '2017-07-01 13:04:13', '2017-07-01 13:04:13', '', 0, 'http://localhost/monochrome/?page_id=11663', 0, 'page', '', 0),
