(11783, 1, '2017-02-17 13:31:47', '2017-02-17 13:31:47', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<div class=\"page-header\">\r\n<h1>Services</h1>\r\n</div>\r\nMonochrome Marketing is a <strong>disruptive marketing consulting firm</strong> that unleashes our experience and capabilities on <strong>small to medium sized businesses</strong> who are seeking high growth. We specialist in companies that would like to jump to the next level, and know that they need strong, creative marketing capabilities to get there.\r\n\r\nWith more than <strong>350 marketing strategies</strong> developed over 11 years, Monochrome Marketing is one of the most experienced marketing firms in Australia today. Operating nationally with offices in Melbourne, Sydney, Brisbane and Charters Towers, we give companies the ability to outsource their marketing needs to one company, with all services in-house and a no-outsourcing policy.\r\n\r\nCollaborative by nature, Monochrome Marketing has in-house marketing managers, marketing executives, public relations experts, journalists, graphic design, branding, web, SEO and marketing automation specialists - the only marketing services company in Australia to do so in our space.\r\n\r\nWe keep up-to-date with the latest in marketing techniques and technologies, bringing to our clients a sophisticated lead generation platform that powers performance.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Services New', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '11665-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-02-17 13:31:47', '2017-02-17 13:31:47', '', 11665, 'http://localhost/monochrome/2017/02/17/11665-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
