(11954, 1, '2017-07-01 10:39:38', '2017-07-01 10:39:38', '[vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" css=\".vc_custom_1488775792089{background-image: url(http://monochromemarketing.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/banner1.jpg?id=11679) !important;background-position: 0 0 !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;}\" el_class=\"back-size\"][vc_column width=\"2/3\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"MARKETING CONSULTANCY\" font_container=\"tag:h1|text_align:left|color:%23ffffff\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Oxygen%3A300%2Cregular%2C700|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"2/3\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"color: #ffffff; text-align: justify;\">Hello. I’m Claire, owner and sole proprietor of Monochrome Marketing, and I’d like to tell you a little about what I do here, and more importantly what I can do for you.</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #ffffff; text-align: justify;\">I work with business owners, entrepreneurs and professionals of all kinds to create effective marketing strategies which drive new sales. I have many years of experience and I know just about all there is to know about effective marketing off and online, including your website(s), social media channels and mobile devices.</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #ffffff; text-align: justify;\">I can offer a one-off consultancy to help give your business the boost and tools it needs to move forward or as most people prefer, work with you on a monthly basis to continually support and action all of your marketing needs. You can look at the packages page for my most basic option.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\" css=\".vc_custom_1486387245193{background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.7) !important;*background-color: rgb(0,0,0) !important;}\" el_class=\"contact-banner\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"cont-height\"][contact-form-7 id=\"11684\" title=\"Home Banner\"][/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_text_separator title=\"What I Do\" title_align=\"separator_align_left\" color=\"black\" style=\"double\" el_class=\"what-we\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"INSIGHT\" font_container=\"tag:h2|text_align:center|color:%2300bcd4\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Oxygen%3A300%2Cregular%2C700|font_style:700%20bold%20regular%3A700%3Anormal\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\" data-fontsize=\"18\" data-lineheight=\"27\">I use my experience and market knowledge to help you really reach your intended audience, and in the way that will raise the best response.</h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"STRATEGY\" font_container=\"tag:h2|text_align:center|color:%2300bcd4\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Oxygen%3A300%2Cregular%2C700|font_style:700%20bold%20regular%3A700%3Anormal\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">I’ll help you understand the marketing challenges you face, then help you create a strategy that will overcome them effectively and efficiently.</h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"ANALYTICS\" font_container=\"tag:h2|text_align:center|color:%2300bcd4\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Oxygen%3A300%2Cregular%2C700|font_style:700%20bold%20regular%3A700%3Anormal\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">I can drill down deep to get the meaningful data you need, and show you how to derive useful, effective business intelligence from it.</h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" css=\".vc_custom_1486818960180{background-color: #dddddd !important;}\"][vc_column][vc_text_separator title=\"My Services\" color=\"black\" el_class=\"what-we\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]<img class=\" wp-image-11701 alignleft\" style=\"width: 90px; border: 2px solid #00bcd4; border-radius: 10%; padding: 5px;\" src=\"http://monochromemarketing.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/outsourced-marketing-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"98\" height=\"90\" />\r\n<h2><strong>Social Media Management </strong></h2>\r\nI know that managing social media can be a total pain! My job is to make this simple for you and ensure that you have high impact and client specific content[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]<img class=\" wp-image-11701 alignleft\" style=\"width: 90px; border: 2px solid #00bcd4; border-radius: 10%; padding: 5px;\" src=\"http://monochromemarketing.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/marketing-consultancy-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"98\" height=\"90\" />\r\n<h2><strong>Consultancy</strong></h2>\r\nI can supply a full marketing consultancy package designed to establish clear goals and maximize the ROI of your marketing budget, no matter how big or small it may be. [/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" css=\".vc_custom_1486819041284{background-color: #dddddd !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]<img class=\" wp-image-11701 alignleft qknhxuuocxvceiylpyhc\" style=\"width: 90px; border: 2px solid #00bcd4; border-radius: 10%; padding: 5px;\" src=\"http://monochromemarketing.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/google-adwords-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"98\" height=\"90\" />\r\n<h2><strong>Google Adwords</strong></h2>\r\nGoogle Adwords and other pay-per-click campaigns can result in a massive influx of visitors to your site. I can help you achieve that for a lot less than you might think.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]<img class=\" wp-image-11701 alignleft\" style=\"width: 90px; border: 2px solid #00bcd4; border-radius: 10%; padding: 5px;\" src=\"http://monochromemarketing.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Video-Marketing-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"98\" height=\"90\" />\r\n<h2><strong>Video Marketing</strong></h2>\r\nThe use of video as a mainstream marketing tool is increasing exponentially, the benefits of video are now so clear...[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" css=\".vc_custom_1486819052824{background-color: #dddddd !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]<img class=\" wp-image-11701 alignleft\" style=\"width: 90px; border: 2px solid #00bcd4; border-radius: 10%; padding: 5px;\" src=\"http://monochromemarketing.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/search-engine-optimization-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"98\" height=\"90\" />\r\n<h2><strong>Search Engine Optimization</strong></h2>\r\nSearch Engine Optimization is the art of gaining high visibility on Google and other search engines without paying for the privilege. It is tricky, but can be extremely effective. [/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]<img class=\" wp-image-11701 alignleft\" style=\"width: 90px; border: 2px solid #00bcd4; border-radius: 10%; padding: 5px;\" src=\"http://monochromemarketing.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/website-design-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"98\" height=\"90\" />\r\n<h2><strong>Website Design</strong></h2>\r\nIt is not enough today to get your website in front of visitors, you have to engage with them, and offer them the experience they demand. I can help you do just that. [/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Home New', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '11661-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-07-01 10:39:38', '2017-07-01 10:39:38', '', 11661, 'http://monochromemarketing.co.uk/11661-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(11955, 1, '2017-07-01 10:43:11', '2017-07-01 10:43:11', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3 style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><strong>PACKAGES</strong></h3>\r\n<p class=\"justify\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">A helping hand</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">From £350 per month**</p>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">I know that I can be a total nightmare to keep your marketing activity ticking along when you become so busy with your day-to-day job. That is why I offer a monthly marketing package. Included in this price:</p>\r\n<p class=\"justify\"><strong>Social Media</strong>\r\nI will update your social media accounts up to three times a week with engaging content for your followers*</p>\r\n<p class=\"justify\"><strong>Website Updates</strong>\r\nI will update your website with new ‘news’ or ‘blog’ posts once a week*</p>\r\n<p class=\"justify\"><strong>Google Analytic Review</strong>\r\nI will review your Google Analytics account monthly and report back any changes or issues. I will also ensure that if there are any changes needed they are action-ed.</p>\r\n<p class=\"justify\"><strong>Competitor Online Activity Tracking</strong>\r\nI will keep our ear to the ground to keep a track of what your competitors are doing, and report back anything of interest.</p>\r\n<p class=\"justify\"><strong>Monthly Marketing Meeting</strong>\r\nI will use this time to plan for the following month (nobody knows your business better than you, so this will be key to ensuring you are getting the most from me)</p>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">I can offer bespoke packages to suit your business needs just give me a call or send an email to find out more.</p>\r\n* Content to be provided by the client in advance. I will proof read, ensure it is social media friendly, edit and will post to social media accounts and your website on your behalf.\r\n\r\n** Price of £350 per month applies to a minimum 6 month contract[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Just Packages', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '11953-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-07-01 10:43:11', '2017-07-01 10:43:11', '', 11953, 'http://monochromemarketing.co.uk/11953-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(11956, 1, '2017-07-01 10:44:13', '2017-07-01 10:44:13', '[vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\"][vc_column][rev_slider_vc alias=\"about-us\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<p class=\"justify\">To start with, Monochrome isn’t a ‘we’, it’s a ‘me’. I am the Owner, Founder, and Head Cook and Bottle Washer here. It is very much a one-woman-show, and I’d like to talk to you for a moment about why that is such a good thing for you.</p>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">I specialist in providing not just personalized but personal service. I’m the only person you’ll talk to on the phone, the only one who will handle your account, and the only one responsible for giving you outstanding results. When I am working on your account, I am working in your account! When you deal with Monochrome Marketing, you are dealing with me, personally, every time, and I absolutely promise to do right by you on every single task, great or small.</p>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">Now, that is not to say what I do isn’t entirely of a professional caliber, or that you’ll get anything less than state of the art, truly exceptional services. I may only have been in business for myself since 2012, but I have many years of marketing experience under my belt, and I have learned from some of the most respected names in the industry – what better way to become one myself, after all?</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'About Us New', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '11663-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-07-01 10:44:13', '2017-07-01 10:44:13', '', 11663, 'http://monochromemarketing.co.uk/11663-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
