(11965, 1, '2017-07-01 12:46:51', '2017-07-01 12:46:51', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]Whatever your needs are I can help. Social media has all but taken over and become an essential tool for businesses to reach current and potential customers. That being said there are many examples of it being used in the wrong way. This is where I can help. My job is to make sure that the right messages get delivered in the correct format and the right time!\r\n\r\nDepending on your requirements I can create, curate and collate content that portray the story you want to tell in a way your audience will respond to, or I can proof read and rewrite/edit content that you provide.\r\n\r\nI can also manage you social advertising for you to an agreed budget. Doing this helps to increase your reach to customers who have shown an interest in your product or service. Using clever targeting helps to stop wasting money on adverts and gets you seen by the right people.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Social Media Management', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '11746-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-07-01 12:46:51', '2017-07-01 12:46:51', '', 11746, 'http://monochromemarketing.co.uk/11746-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
