(11968, 1, '2017-07-01 13:11:13', '2017-07-01 13:11:13', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]Monochrome Marketing can provide a solid marketing consultancy support to your company. My job is to ensure that I provide a consultancy service tailored to your businesses individual requirements to ensure I meet your business needs and your objectives. Here is a range of ways in which I am able to provide consultancy services within your business.\r\n\r\n<b>Marketing Plan </b>\r\n\r\nThe marketing planning process identifies the future growth potential for a business, with a plan of how this can be achieved. Rigorous research and development of a marketing plan will ensure that a company is best placed to maximise its opportunities in a structured way.\r\n\r\nEach marketing plan will vary to reflect the business involved, however many of the following elements are likely to be included:-\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Competitors</li>\r\n 	<li>Products</li>\r\n 	<li>Price structure</li>\r\n 	<li>Target market</li>\r\n 	<li>Branding</li>\r\n 	<li>Routes to market</li>\r\n 	<li>Objectives</li>\r\n 	<li>Strategy</li>\r\n 	<li>Activity plan</li>\r\n 	<li>Resource required</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<b>Monthly Consultant Forum </b>\r\n\r\nA regular opportunity to discuss the development of your business. Many growing companies may not be in a position to employ a full-time marketing manager but are at the point where they really need to start pushing marketing. I will come to you business and hold a forum where we can look at business performance, success and achievement of objectives over recent months and develop new strategies and objectives for future development, supported by a detailed action plan.\r\n\r\n<b>One Off Project</b>\r\n\r\nProjects may include new product development and launch, new market development or new routes to market. Whatever your project Sharp Marketing are able to provide focus, an independent viewpoint and a great depth of strategic experience to ensure that the project is completed diligently and to your timetable.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Consultancy', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '11748-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-07-01 13:11:13', '2017-07-01 13:11:13', '', 11748, 'http://monochromemarketing.co.uk/11748-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
